properties.areaDesc: Coastal waters from Tarpon Springs to Suwannee River FL out 20 NM
properties.headline: Dense Fog Advisory issued January 16 at 11:18AM EST until January 17 at 12:00AM EST by NWS Tampa Bay Ruskin FL
properties.description:
* WHAT...Dense fog will reduce visibility to less than one mile.

* WHERE...Coastal waters from Tarpon Springs to Suwannee River
FL out 20 NM.

* WHEN...Until midnight tonight.

* IMPACTS...Low visibility due to sea fog will make navigation
difficult.
properties.instruction:
If you must navigate, proceed with caution. Use proper fog
signals. Make sure all running lights are on. Remember to use
your radar and compass.

NWSheadline: MARINE DENSE FOG ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL MIDNIGHT TONIGHT
